# WordPress Fast Deploy - Git Attributes
# Ensures consistent line endings across Windows/Linux/Mac

# Shell scripts and config files should always use LF (Unix) line endings
*.sh text eol=lf
config.sh text eol=lf

# Batch files should use CRLF (Windows) line endings  
*.bat text eol=crlf

# Markdown and documentation can use native line endings
*.md text
*.txt text

# Binary files
*.jpg binary
*.png binary
*.gif binary
